Special Internet Homepage Opens in U.S. to Praise Songun Policy 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, January 26 (KCNA) --The U.S. Group for the Study of the Songun Politics opened a special Internet homepage on Jan. 1 to praise the great Songun policy.
 Posted on the homepage are an article praising the historic long journey of Songun made by leader Kim Jong Il contributed by John Paul Cupp, chairman of the group, articles introducing the essence and vitality of the policy and nearly 20 photos titled �gSongun history seen through photos�h. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chairman in his article said Kim Jong Il has resolutely defied the wanton threat and pressure of the U.S. imperialists and reactionaries with his treasured sword called Songun. He continued: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Recorded in the history are the disgraceful defeats the great sun of Songun has inflicted upon the imperialists. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Korean socialism has stood as a fortress defending independence and achieving prosperity, throwing bright rays all over the world, and the cause of Korea�fs reunification and the cause of global independence and the cause against imperialism and the U.S. has dynamically advanced, valiantly meeting all challenges. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Progressive humankind are loudly shouting �gLong live General Kim Jong Il, the greatest sun of Songun!�h and �gLong live the great Songun politics! �g looking up to Korea, the homeland of the Songun politics. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The article stressed the historic significance of December 24 in carrying out the revolutionary cause of Juche as it is the day Kim Jong Il assumed the supreme commandership of the Korean People�fs Army and anti-Japanese war hero Kim Jong Suk was born

Friendly Gathering with Chinese Embassy Officials 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, January 26 (KCNA) -- The DPRK Foreign Ministry arranged a friendly gathering with officials of the Chinese embassy in Pyongyang Tuesday on the occasion of the New Year Juche 94 (2005).
 Present there on invitation were Chinese Ambassador Wu Donghe and embassy officials. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Minister Paek Nam Sun, Vice-Minister Kim Hyong Jun and officials of the ministry were on hand. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  The participants in the gathering chatted about the friendly and cooperative relations between the two countries, deepening the feelings of friendship.

Might of Unity in One Mind Grows under Songun Banner 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, January 26 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun Wednesday dedicates an article to the 20th anniversary of the publication of leader Kim Jong Il's famous work "Let's Advance Holding High the Banner of Single-Minded Unity".
 The work, brought out on January 26, Juche 74 (1985), expounds a wide range of matters from the importance of unity in one mind in the revolutionary struggle and the foundation of close and mighty unity in one mind to the need to further consolidate this unity, an ever-victorious banner. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In the period of "the arduous march" it was eloquently demonstrated that the unity of the people in the Songun revolution is a unity that grows hundred-fold stronger and displays great might when ordeals increase, a unity more powerful than the nuclear weapons, declares the author of the article, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Unity in Songun revolution is an unbreakable integral whole which has been consolidated with the strong revolutionary army of Mt. Paektu as the backbone. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Now in the DPRK the People's Army is the core of unity in one mind, the army which has been strengthened into an army strong in idea and faith, a matchless powerful army, under the energetic leadership of Kim Jong Il. Our unity has been strengthened immensely and is displaying its great might as the powerful revolutionary army is faithfully upholding the idea and leadership of the headquarters of the revolution in the van, the army which finds its physical quality in and highly displays the spirit of devotedly defending the leader, the spirit of devotedly carrying through his instructions and the spirit of heroic sacrifice. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Unity in the Songun revolution is also an integral whole of the entire Party, and army and all the people united in idea and purpose on the basis of the great Songun idea and a moral crystal based on comradeship and sense of obligation of those holding arms. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The army and people of the DPRK are now proud of being unquestioned followers, resolute defenders and steadfast implementers of the Songun idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
The ideological viewpoint, fighting morale and mode of life of the people have   changed beyond recognition and the integration of the army and people in idea and spirit and in fighting morale have been achieved in the course of carrying through the Songun idea with it as their creed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A big army of revolutionary soldiers, who, charmed by the fervent comradeship of Kim Jong Il, fight in defense of their faith and sense of obligation to the leader even on an isolated island, have grown and the whole country is overflowing with the noble traits of laying down one's own life for society, collective and comrades without hesitation and breaking through ordeals, helping and leading each other forward.
